      • getAuthor

        public Contact getAuthor()
        The getAuthor() method returns an instance of the Contact that authored the message. This method should only be used to get the author of a message when the ContactType of the getFrom() method is ContactType.CHANNEL or ContactType.GROUP.
        Returns:
        The Contact that authored the message.

      • getFrom

        public Contact getFrom()
        The getFrom() method returns an instance of the Contact that is sending the user the message. If the ContactType is ContactType.CHANNEL or ContactType.GROUP, the returned contact will be the Channel or Group, respectively. To get the original author of the message, use the getAuthor() method.
        Returns:
        The Contact that is sending the message.

      • isActive

        public boolean isActive()
        The isActive() method determines if the MessageIn is in progress.
        Returns:
        boolean indicating if the message is currently active.

      • reset

        public void reset()
        The reset() method resets the MessageIn instance back to the default values.
